 Since the company was founded in 2016 

00:00:09.550 --> 00:00:12.309
 We have published many self-image applications 

00:00:12.310 --> 00:00:14.969
 And participation across social networks in the global market. 

00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:18.529
 Our first application, Sweet Selfie, 

00:00:18.530 --> 00:00:22.488
 Million active users per day in less than 3 months 

00:00:22.755 --> 00:00:25.419
 Highlighted on Google Play. 

